nodes.text: Nooranbakarakana was a Frozian Jedi who served the Jedi Order during the High Republic Era. Jedi Master Stellan Gios, who knew Nooranbakarakana by reputation alone, spotted the Frozian among many Jedi who attended the Valo Republic Fair. Later, during the Nihil attack on Valo, Nooranbakarakana was among the assembled Jedi and Galactic Republic forces who checked in with Gios after Padawan Ram Jomaram restored communications channels.
